00:56:09.866 --> 00:56:14.686
but I know there's
workshops going on

00:56:14.686 --> 00:56:19.846
and so it's been an effort
by students in the UCs

00:56:20.066 --> 00:56:22.316
to shift the food purchase
of the UC system, right,

00:56:22.546 --> 00:56:25.466
so that's another example.

